zh: Fake\SuperSonia是一款由玩家原创内#容构成的平台冒险游戏,#按Z打开创意工坊订阅地图吧
en: Fake/SuperSonia is a platform adventure game # composed of original content.# Now, let's press Z to see other people's highlights

引索: 没有保存 是否继续编辑
zh: 没有保存 是否继续编辑?
en: This map is not saved. Do you want to continue editing?
Do you want to continue editing?

zh: 墙#地图的基本构成元素，无法被穿透。
en: Block#The basic elements of the map that can not be penetrated

zh: 跳床#接触后可以触发角色的跳跃
en: latform#Can trigger a jump of the character

zh: 沙板#用沙子构成的挡板，接触后会很快消失。
en: Fade Block#A fade block made of sand that will soon disappear after touch

zh: 存档#接触后会保存当前位置，下一次死亡时会传送回上一个存档点。
en: Save#Touch to save the current location，the next death will be sent back to the last Save.

zh: 尖刺#经典障碍之一，碰触即死。按A可以设置朝向。
en: Spike#One of the classic obstacles，touch then dead.# Press A to set the orientation.

zh: 出生点#玩家的初始出生点。按快捷键Enter可以进入测试模式，从出生点出发。
en: Born#The initial point of birth of the player. #Press the shortcut key Enter to enter the test mode，starting from the birth point.

zh: 跳台#按↓+Jump可以跳入下一层。
en: Platform#Press ↓ + Jump to jump to the down space.

zh: 终点#抵达至此完成关卡。每个关卡都必需终点。
en: End#Arrive at this to finish a level. Each level must have an end.

zh: 炮台#向玩家所在位置发射子弹，碰触到子弹即死。#默认延迟0，按A可以调整延迟，每个红灯会让炮台增加0.25秒的发射延迟，#最高可设置增加1.5秒发射延迟。
en: Fort#To the player's location to launch bullets， touch the bullet will let character dead. #The default transmission delay is 0， according to A can adjust the delay， each red light will let the Fort has a 0.25 second transmission delay  up to 1.5 seconds to set the transmission delay.
